These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: purple, amber, blue, black, blood-red, fuchsia
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, cycling, cricket, baseball, snowboarding
 1. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
 2. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the right of the person who likes amber##5
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes blue##1
 6. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who likes amber##1
 8. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
10. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
11. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4    |    5     |  6   |
| Color      | blue | black   | blood-red | purple | amber    | fuchsia  |
| Sport   | baseball  | cricket | snowboarding   | biathlon  | rowing | cycling |

