.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, chinese, russian, spanish, indonesian
6 different pets are kept: frog, pony, guinea-pig, turtle, ferret, chinchilla
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the spanish##5
 2. the canadian is on the left of the colombian##1
 3. the chinese is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 4. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the indonesian##1
 6. the russian is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the chinese is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the colombian is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the chinese##1
10. the russian is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
11. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
13. the spanish is the owner of the frog##1
14. the canadian is on the left or right of the colombian##3
15. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
16. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |     3      |       4       |     5      |   6    |
| Nationality   | spanish | indonesian | chinese | canadian         | colombian | russian |
| Pet   | frog    | ferret      | guinea-pig      | turtle | pony   | chinchilla |

