.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-3::.
City: rome, berlin, hamburg, london, nizza, miami
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: epic, disaster, family, animation, drama, romance
 1. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 2. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
 3. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 9. the person watching family movies is between the person traveling to miami and the person watching romance movies##2
10. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3    |    4     |    5    |    6     |
| City      | miami | rome | nizza   | london | berlin   | hamburg |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | family         | romance | drama     | epic | animation     |

