 3. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 4. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
 5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
 6. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 9. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
10. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
11. the cain-smoker is the person playing chess##1
12. the cain-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |       4       |    5    |       6       |
| Game   | monopoly | poker  | chess | backgammon     | snooker | mah-jongg        |
| Cigar         | dunhill | aristoff | cain    | ritmeester | old-henry  | tiparillo |

