 2. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
 3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 4. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 5. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 6. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 7. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating zucchini##2
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 9. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
10. the person eating lettuce is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating zucchini##2
11. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
12. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
14. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
15. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
