.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-9::.
House: modern, wooden, tower, cape-cod, palace, gothic-revival
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, sprite, almond-milk
 1. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
 2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 5. the modern house is the modern house##1
 6. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the tower house##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
 9. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
10. the gothic-revival house is between the tower house and the person drinking almond-milk##2
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
12. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the wooden house##1
13. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
14. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
15. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
16. the person drinking water is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |    3     |     4      |    5    |   6    |
| House   | cape-cod | wooden | palace | tower     | gothic-revival | modern |
| Beverage     | sprite  | water      | soy-milk      | hot-chocolate | coffee  | almond-milk    |

