 5. the person who's sport is rugby is the colonial house##1
 6. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 8. the colonial house is in an even position##4
 9. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
10. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
12. the wooden house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
13. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5     |       6       |
| House   | farmhouse  | colonial        | craftsman  | cape-cod     | wooden | ranch-style |
| Sport       | swimming | rugby | volleyball | cycling | cricket  | basketball          |

