.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-20::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, swimming, volleyball, water-polo, golf, biathlon
There are 6 different nationalities: turkish, nigerian, spanish, argentine, mexican, thai
 1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 2. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the nigerian##1
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is the mexican##1
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the nigerian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 8. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the mexican##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the thai##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Sport         | biathlon    | water-polo | swimming   | volleyball | baseball    | golf |
| Nationality   | turkish | thai  | mexican | spanish      | argentine | nigerian    |

 